reviews.review_text: long long long ,,,hey .....crazy night! ok ,,so far just checked out the stanger,, very purdy:))

Love this show So glad I came across this. I have an old cassette of this show, but the quality here is obviously much better. I was there and still love the beginning of the second set through Eyes. That Eyes has a different "swing" to it, if you will. Thanks so much for sharing!
